---
title: Open Governance
summary: Public roadmaps, accountability, and transparent decision-making for accountable stewardship. 
eyebrow: Open
order: 2
---

We believe in open governance as a core principle of our work. By maintaining public roadmaps, fostering transparent decision-making processes, and holding ourselves accountable to the community, we ensure that Sonicverse remains a collaborative and inclusive ecosystem. Our commitment to open governance allows us to build trust, encourage participation, and create software that truly serves the needs of independent media creators.